Nonatthi-novigataduka
Kusalattika
Paṭiccavāra
Paccayapaccanīya
Saṅkhyāvāra
Nonatthi-novigataduka
63.
275Nonatthipaccayā…  novigatapaccayā nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā pañca, naanantare pañca, nasamanantare pañca, naaññamaññe pañca, naupanissaye pañca, napurejāte pañca, napacchājāte pañca, naāsevane pañca, nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke pañca, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte ekaṃ, nonatthiyā pañca.
